PrecisAppointment of KENT WILLIAM ROACH, C.M., of Toronto, Ontario, to be a part-time member of the Management Advisory Board for the Royal Canadian Mounted Police, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years; and his designation as Chairperson of the Management Advisory Board for the Royal Canadian Mounted Police.
